[scenario]
description="Hundreds of years ago, the defeated Sorcerer Kesorak was entombed here, along with a number of his followers. An unholy chill now encircles the tombs, and many believe that the voice of Kesorak can still be heard, whispering amongst the withered trees of this barren landscape. Unconcerned by their gloomy surroundings, your leaders have chosen this place to clash."
